{"id":168,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":168,"title":"2 Corinthians 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","Bring every thought into obedience—Paul glories in the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.1","order":"03.10.010.19037"},["b","1"],"Now I Paul myself beseech you by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"meekness"],"and gentleness of Christ, who in presence",["i","am"],"base among you, but being absent am bold toward you:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.2","order":"03.10.010.19038"},["b","2"],"But I beseech",["i","you,"],"that I may not be bold when I am present with that confidence, wherewith I think to be bold against some, which think of us as if we walked according to the flesh."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.3","order":"03.10.010.19039"},["b","3"],"For though we walk in the flesh, we do not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"war"],"after the flesh:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.4","order":"03.10.010.19040"},["b","4"],"(For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"weapons"],"of our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"warfare"],["i","are"],"not carnal, but mighty through God to the pulling down of strong holds;)"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.5","order":"03.10.010.19041"},["b","5"],"Casting down imaginations, and every high thing that exalteth itself against the knowledge of God, and bringing into captivity every",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"thought"],"to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"obedience"],"of Christ;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.6","order":"03.10.010.19042"},["b","6"],"And having in a readiness to revenge all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"disobedience"],", when your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"obedience"],"is fulfilled."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.7","order":"03.10.010.19043"},["b","7"],"Do ye look on things after the outward",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"appearance"],"? If any man trust to himself that he is Christ’s, let him of himself think this again, that, as he",["i","is"],"Christ’s, even so",["i","are"],"we",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Christ’s"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.8","order":"03.10.010.19044"},["b","8"],"For though I should boast somewhat more of our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"authority"],", which the Lord hath given us for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"edification"],", and not for your destruction, I should not be ashamed:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.9","order":"03.10.010.19045"},["b","9"],"That I may not seem as if I would terrify you by letters."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.10","order":"03.10.010.19046"},["b","10"],"For",["i","his"],"letters, say they,",["i","are"],"weighty and powerful; but",["i","his"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"bodily"],"presence",["i","is"],"weak, and",["i","his"],"speech",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"contemptible"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.11","order":"03.10.010.19047"},["b","11"],"Let such an one think this, that, such as we are in word by letters when we are absent, such",["i","will we be"],"also in deed when we are present."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.12","order":"03.10.010.19048"},["b","12"],"For we dare not make ourselves of the number, or compare ourselves with some that commend themselves: but they measuring themselves by themselves, and comparing themselves among themselves, are not wise."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.13","order":"03.10.010.19049"},["b","13"],"But we will not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"boast"],"of things without",["i","our"],"measure, but according to the measure of the rule which God hath distributed to us, a measure to reach even unto you."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.14","order":"03.10.010.19050"},["b","14"],"For we stretch not ourselves beyond",["i","our measure,"],"as though we reached not unto you: for we are come as far as to you also in",["i","preaching"],"the gospel of Christ:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.15","order":"03.10.010.19051"},["b","15"],"Not boasting of things without",["i","our"],"measure,",["i","that is,"],"of other men’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"labours"],"; but having hope, when your faith is increased, that we shall be enlarged by you according to our rule abundantly,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.16","order":"03.10.010.19052"},["b","16"],"To preach the gospel in the",["i","regions"],"beyond you,",["i","and"],"not to boast in another man’s line of things made ready to our hand."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.17","order":"03.10.010.19053"},["b","17"],"But he that glorieth, let him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"glory"],"in the Lord."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.18","order":"03.10.010.19054"},["b","18"],"For not he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"commendeth"],"himself is approved, but whom the Lord commendeth."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.1a","order":"03.10.010.19055"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.23"},"D&C 19:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.5.5,14"},"25:5 (5, 14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.3a","order":"03.10.010.19057"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/war"},"TG War"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.4a","order":"03.10.010.19059"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/6.11.10-24"},"Eph. 6:11 (10–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.4b","order":"03.10.010.19061"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.7"},"1 Cor. 9:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.5a","order":"03.10.010.19063"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/motivations"},"TG Motivations"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.5b","order":"03.10.010.19065"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/obedience"},"TG Obedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.6a","order":"03.10.010.19067"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.6b","order":"03.10.010.19069"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/7.15"},"2 Cor. 7:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.7a","order":"03.10.010.19071"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.7"},"1 Sam. 16:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.7b","order":"03.10.010.19073"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/3.23"},"1 Cor. 3:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.8a","order":"03.10.010.19075"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.10"},"2 Cor. 13:10"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.8b","order":"03.10.010.19077"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/edification"},"TG Edification"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.10a","order":"03.10.010.19079"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.13"},"Gal. 4:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.10b","order":"03.10.010.19081"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.6"},"2 Cor. 11:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.13a","order":"03.10.010.19083"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/boast"},"TG Boast"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.15a","order":"03.10.010.19085"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.20"},"Rom. 15:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.17a","order":"03.10.010.19087"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.24.23-24"},"Jer. 9:24 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.16.11-16"},"Alma 26:16 (11–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.18a","order":"03.10.010.19089"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/18.14"},"Luke 18:14"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/boast"},"TG Boast"],"."]]}
